<i>My lover and me</i>

705
00:44:35,200 --> 00:44:37,960
<i>My lover and me...</i>

706
00:44:39,080 --> 00:44:41,520
Looks like you're having a hard time too.

707
00:44:43,880 --> 00:44:44,840
Is it that obvious?

